data.description:
MUST SEE! 18+- acre ranch nestled in East Texas. Property features a custom built ranch style-3 bedroom, 3.5 bath house with two car carport that is gated and fenced. Home boasts commercial gas stove with dual ovens, stainless steel appliances, custom metal built oven hood, quartz counter tops, laminate wood floors, and a covered porch that wraps completely around this home. House comes with above ground swimming pool with custom built deck. Shop is 40x30 with 22 ft ceilings, 12x10 doors. There is also additional room above carport that has air-heat, and property has it's own well.
Agent Remarks: Please give 24 hour notice. Listing Agent or Seller will be present at showings.
